Atroa is the Bringer of Spring, Wind-Daughter, Provider, Shy One, First Sister of the wind-gods of Oerth. Her portfolio includes Spring, East Wind, and Renewal. The sister of Velnius, Telchur, Sotillion, and Wenta and daughter of Procan, she is romantically linked to Fharlanghn after she was rejected by Kurell. 
Atroa's Realm, the Grove of Perpetual Spring, is in Brux in the Beastlands. She is also thought to spend time in Morninglory, the Realm of Lathander and Ushas. 

